<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a18Feb1937"><font color="red">18 February 1937</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Viscount Carlow):  My piece about the Norwegian captain and the tailor was swamped out in the Ohio floods (<i>transition</i> this time being printed in Cincinnati) but it has been reset and I believe they have now given it a second <i>bon &agrave; tirer</i>. </div>
